											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player emerges from the strange portal. They see Ptaris stood at the end of the wooden pier projecting out into the basement. He stands with his back to the player, perfectly still. At his feet is the body of Esther the expeditioner. As he speaks he turns to face the player.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Esther the expeditioner: S_GLO_Expeditioner_5f4048ba-72ef-43c2-9528-1c9a12f3f82f" />
